message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
authors:
  - family-names: Tota
    given-names: Praneeth
title: "Adaptive Utility Agents: A Framework for Self-Optimizing AI Systems"
version: 0.4
date-released: 2026-04-04
license: GPL-3.0
license-url: "https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html"
url: "https://github.com/praneethtota/Adaptive-Utility-Agent"
abstract: >
  A framework for wrapping frontier language models with an adaptive utility
  layer governed by a mathematically grounded utility function U = w_e·E +
  w_c·C + w_k·K. Includes a three-layer continual learning pipeline, personality
  system, entity trust system, distributed model graph architecture, Arbiter Agent
  for contradiction resolution, and utility-deviation-triggered blue-green deployment.
